   Quick Change:
   A 1990 Reorganization
   At Hewlett-Packard
   Already Is Paying Off
   ---
   HP Cuts Bureaucracy, Costs,
   Undoing Past Blunders,
   2 Striking New Computers
   ---
   Staffers Fret Over `Excessing'
   ----
   By Stephen Kreider Yoder
