   Technology:
   Compaq, Microsoft Plan Industry Group
   To Create Standard for Workstations
   ----
   By Jim Bartimo and Stephen Kreider Yoder
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/11/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
<CO>
   CPQ MSFT SUNW DEC INTC MOT MIPS
</CO>
<IN>
